'''Collin''' is Charlotte's assistant.

==History==
Collin was Charlotte's assistant. When Cooper came to her office to return her things, Charlotte said to get out and Cooper pointed out that she meant for him to get out.

He later went upstairs to [[Oceanside Wellness Group]] to get [[Leah Hudley|Leah Hudley's]] files for [[Wyatt Lockhart]].

==Career==
He is an assistant to [[Charlotte King]].
